run 'npm i mongoose'

write a connection script and use this below connection string
  mongoose.connect( connectionString )



steps to create a collection for an entity

  create a schema
  create a model using the schema, and register it with Mongoose


schema: defines the shape of the entity instance - e.g. what fields a restaurant document contain
        it includes fields for a document of the entity, the data type of the fields, validation if any



model: a class created using the corresponding schema
       has methods to make DB queries - e.g. find list of restaurants, add a new restaurant etc.